[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":657},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Freact\u002F20221008\u002F1445725227\u002F":3,"page:\u002Freact\u002F20221008\u002F1445725227\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Freact\u002F20221008\u002F1445725227\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Freact\u002F20221008\u002F1445725227\u002F":632,"related:\u002Freact\u002F20221008\u002F1445725227\u002F":641},"\u002Fen\u002Freact\u002F2022\u002F10\u002F08\u002Freact-day-24-react-router-basics-intro\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":614,"date":615,"description":18,"extension":616,"lang":617,"meta":618,"navigation":205,"path":619,"readingMinutes":620,"seo":621,"standalone":622,"stem":623,"tags":624,"tldr":629,"updated":629,"url":630,"__hash__":631},"content\u002F終究都要學 React 何不現在學呢？\u002F24-終究都要學-React-何不現在學呢？-React-Router-router-基礎與介紹.md","終究都要學 React 何不現在學呢？ - React Router - 基礎與介紹 - (24)","1445725227",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":607},"minimark",[11,15,19,23,26,29,32,35,43,59,83,86,95,112,122,125,136,145,149,164,249,252,256,262,267,276,282,291,294,310,316,323,362,368,444,455,464,475,554,560,570,580,588,591,594,603],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"雖然在極小的專案下，前面章節所學的知識點是很足夠的，但是我們在真正的專案開發上不可能只用前面的知識點而已，因為頁面會隨著專案規模大小越來越複雜，因此我們需要一個能夠幫助我們管理頁面的工具，而這個工具就是 React Router。",[12,20,22],{"id":21},"什麼是-react-router","什麼是 React Router？",[16,24,25],{},"React Router 是什麼呢？在說明 React Router 這個之前想先簡單講一個觀念，也就是所謂的 SPA（Single Page Application，中文又稱單頁式應用程式）。",[16,27,28],{},"那麼 SPA 是什麼呢？SPA 是一個 Web 開發實作...",[16,30,31],{},"...\n.....\n.......",[16,33,34],{},"好，暫停一下，其實這一段開始有點文謅謅了，所以我就簡單解釋就好，其實就是從頭到尾你都在同一頁面的意思，什麼叫做同一頁面呢？後面會慢慢解釋。",[16,36,37,38,42],{},"剛剛有提到 SPA 中文是「單頁式應用程式」其實就是你從頭到尾都在 ",[39,40,41],"code",{},"index.html"," 這個頁面上，因此如果是採用 SPA 模式開發的網站，那麼你在瀏覽器的網址列上可能會看到這種形式",[44,45,50],"pre",{"className":46,"code":47,"language":48,"meta":49,"style":49},"language-txt shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","https:\u002F\u002Fwww.example.com\u002F#\u002F\n","txt","",[39,51,52],{"__ignoreMap":49},[53,54,57],"span",{"class":55,"line":56},"line",1,[53,58,47],{},[16,60,61,62,64,65,68,69,71,72,75,76,79,80,82],{},"而這一串就是透過 JavaScript 模擬後端路由形成的 SPA 網頁，那你可能會想說 ",[39,63,41],{}," 呢？怎麼消失了？通常來講 「",[39,66,67],{},"\u002F","」默認是 ",[39,70,41],{},"，因此才可以忽略，但也是有一些網站默認是 ",[39,73,74],{},"default.html","、",[39,77,78],{},"home.html","，而這一段是可以透過伺服器的設置來決定默認首頁是哪一個，但通常默認會是 ",[39,81,41],{},"。",[16,84,85],{},"那麼在 SPA 還沒有流行之前，早期都是使用 MPA （Multi Page Application，中文又稱多頁式應用程式）的方式開發，所以你會看到瀏覽器網址列像這樣子呈現",[44,87,89],{"className":46,"code":88,"language":48,"meta":49,"style":49},"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.example.com\u002Fuser\u002Fprofile\n",[39,90,91],{"__ignoreMap":49},[53,92,93],{"class":55,"line":56},[53,94,88],{},[16,96,97,98,101,102,105,106,108,109,82],{},"而不會有 ",[39,99,100],{},"\u002F#\u002F"," 的形式，因為一段 ",[39,103,104],{},"#\u002F"," 就是由前端模擬後端路由的一種形式，雖然也可以調整成類似 MPA 的路由形式，但這個必須要與後端搭配才可以，因此 SPA 開發上大多還是以 ",[39,107,100],{}," 模擬為主，而這種模式又稱之為 ",[39,110,111],{},"hash mode",[16,113,114,115],{},"但這一點並不是我們要了解的知識，如果想更深入了解的話，可以考慮閱讀我先前寫的這一篇 ",[116,117,121],"a",{"href":118,"rel":119},"https:\u002F\u002Fisraynotarray.com\u002Fother\u002F20210529\u002F2519649612\u002F",[120],"nofollow","淺談 SPA、CSR、SSR、MPA、SSG 專有名詞",[16,123,124],{},"那麼前面對於 SPA 有一個簡單基本概念之後 React Router 就是要幫助我們做這件事情的重要核心，因此接下來你可以打開任何一個專案，例如前面章節我們所建立的 Vite TodoList 專案也可以，並在終端機輸入以下指令安裝 React Router",[44,126,130],{"className":127,"code":128,"language":129,"meta":49,"style":49},"language-cmd shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","npm install --save react-router-dom\n","cmd",[39,131,132],{"__ignoreMap":49},[53,133,134],{"class":55,"line":56},[53,135,128],{},[16,137,138,139,144],{},"而這邊我會使用前面所建立的 ",[116,140,143],{"href":141,"rel":142},"https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fhsiangfeng\u002Fexample-vite-react",[120],"example-vite-react"," 當作示範，你也可以趁機會現在下載或者建立一個新專案。",[12,146,148],{"id":147},"react-router-起手式","React Router 起手式",[16,150,151,152,155,156,159,160,163],{},"首先第一個步驟先打開 App.jsx 引入 ",[39,153,154],{},"import { HashRouter } from \"react-router-dom\";","，而這個 ",[39,157,158],{},"HashRouter"," 本身就是一個元件概念，接著只需要使用它將整個 ",[39,161,162],{},"\u003CApp \u002F>"," 包起來即可",[44,165,169],{"className":166,"code":167,"language":168,"meta":49,"style":49},"language-jsx shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","import React from 'react'\nimport { HashRouter } from \"react-router-dom\";\nimport ReactDOM from 'react-dom\u002Fclient'\nimport App from '.\u002FApp'\nimport '.\u002Findex.css'\n\nReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById('root')).render(\n  \u003CReact.StrictMode>\n    \u003CHashRouter>\n      \u003CApp \u002F>\n    \u003C\u002FHashRouter>\n  \u003C\u002FReact.StrictMode>\n)\n","jsx",[39,170,171,176,182,188,194,200,207,213,219,225,231,237,243],{"__ignoreMap":49},[53,172,173],{"class":55,"line":56},[53,174,175],{},"import React from 'react'\n",[53,177,179],{"class":55,"line":178},2,[53,180,181],{},"import { HashRouter } from \"react-router-dom\";\n",[53,183,185],{"class":55,"line":184},3,[53,186,187],{},"import ReactDOM from 'react-dom\u002Fclient'\n",[53,189,191],{"class":55,"line":190},4,[53,192,193],{},"import App from '.\u002FApp'\n",[53,195,197],{"class":55,"line":196},5,[53,198,199],{},"import '.\u002Findex.css'\n",[53,201,203],{"class":55,"line":202},6,[53,204,206],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":205},true,"\n",[53,208,210],{"class":55,"line":209},7,[53,211,212],{},"ReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById('root')).render(\n",[53,214,216],{"class":55,"line":215},8,[53,217,218],{},"  \u003CReact.StrictMode>\n",[53,220,222],{"class":55,"line":221},9,[53,223,224],{},"    \u003CHashRouter>\n",[53,226,228],{"class":55,"line":227},10,[53,229,230],{},"      \u003CApp \u002F>\n",[53,232,234],{"class":55,"line":233},11,[53,235,236],{},"    \u003C\u002FHashRouter>\n",[53,238,240],{"class":55,"line":239},12,[53,241,242],{},"  \u003C\u002FReact.StrictMode>\n",[53,244,246],{"class":55,"line":245},13,[53,247,248],{},")\n",[16,250,251],{},"恭喜你！你已經成功引入了 React Router 囉！接下來我們就可以開始使用它了。",[12,253,255],{"id":254},"react-router-基本使用","React Router 基本使用",[16,257,258,259,82],{},"接下來我們要來認識另一個東西，也就是 ",[39,260,261],{},"Route",[16,263,264,266],{},[39,265,261],{}," 主要是用來定義路徑跟 Components 之間的關係，你也可以把它想像成「綁定」的概念，舉例來講如果你希望使用者訪問的路徑是以下",[44,268,270],{"className":46,"code":269,"language":48,"meta":49,"style":49},"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.example.com\u002F#\u002Ftodolist\n",[39,271,272],{"__ignoreMap":49},[53,273,274],{"class":55,"line":56},[53,275,269],{},[16,277,278,279,281],{},"那麼你在使用 ",[39,280,261],{}," 的時候就可以這樣寫",[44,283,285],{"className":166,"code":284,"language":168,"meta":49,"style":49},"\u003CRoute path=\"\u002Ftodolist\" element={ \u003CToDoList\u002F> }>\n",[39,286,287],{"__ignoreMap":49},[53,288,289],{"class":55,"line":56},[53,290,284],{},[16,292,293],{},"而常見的屬性主要會有兩個",[295,296,297,304],"ul",{},[298,299,300,303],"li",{},[39,301,302],{},"path","：定義路徑",[298,305,306,309],{},[39,307,308],{},"element","：定義對應的元件",[16,311,312,313,315],{},"到目前為止，這是一個基本的 ",[39,314,261],{}," 使用方式。",[16,317,318,319,322],{},"事不宜遲，就來把原本寫在 App.jsx 的 ",[39,320,321],{},"ToDoList"," 挪出來放到另一個元件內，例如叫做 ToDoList.jsx，而 App.jsx 則改成以下",[44,324,326],{"className":166,"code":325,"language":168,"meta":49,"style":49},"const App = () => {\n  return (\n    \u003Ch1>App\u003C\u002Fh1>\n  )\n}\n\nexport default App;\n",[39,327,328,333,338,343,348,353,357],{"__ignoreMap":49},[53,329,330],{"class":55,"line":56},[53,331,332],{},"const App = () => {\n",[53,334,335],{"class":55,"line":178},[53,336,337],{},"  return (\n",[53,339,340],{"class":55,"line":184},[53,341,342],{},"    \u003Ch1>App\u003C\u002Fh1>\n",[53,344,345],{"class":55,"line":190},[53,346,347],{},"  )\n",[53,349,350],{"class":55,"line":196},[53,351,352],{},"}\n",[53,354,355],{"class":55,"line":202},[53,356,206],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":205},[53,358,359],{"class":55,"line":209},[53,360,361],{},"export default App;\n",[16,363,364,365,367],{},"接下來就是打開 main.jsx 引入 ToDoList.jsx 並搭配 ",[39,366,261],{}," 一起使用",[44,369,371],{"className":166,"code":370,"language":168,"meta":49,"style":49},"import React from 'react'\nimport { HashRouter, Route } from \"react-router-dom\";\nimport ReactDOM from 'react-dom\u002Fclient'\nimport App from '.\u002FApp'\nimport '.\u002Findex.css'\n\nimport ToDoList from \".\u002FTodoList\";\n\nReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById('root')).render(\n  \u003CReact.StrictMode>\n    \u003CHashRouter>\n      \u003CRoute path=\"\u002F\" element={ \u003CApp \u002F> } \u002F>\n      \u003CRoute path=\"\u002Ftodolist\" element={ \u003CToDoList \u002F> } \u002F>\n    \u003C\u002FHashRouter>\n  \u003C\u002FReact.StrictMode>\n)\n",[39,372,373,377,382,386,390,394,398,403,407,411,415,419,424,429,434,439],{"__ignoreMap":49},[53,374,375],{"class":55,"line":56},[53,376,175],{},[53,378,379],{"class":55,"line":178},[53,380,381],{},"import { HashRouter, Route } from \"react-router-dom\";\n",[53,383,384],{"class":55,"line":184},[53,385,187],{},[53,387,388],{"class":55,"line":190},[53,389,193],{},[53,391,392],{"class":55,"line":196},[53,393,199],{},[53,395,396],{"class":55,"line":202},[53,397,206],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":205},[53,399,400],{"class":55,"line":209},[53,401,402],{},"import ToDoList from \".\u002FTodoList\";\n",[53,404,405],{"class":55,"line":215},[53,406,206],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":205},[53,408,409],{"class":55,"line":221},[53,410,212],{},[53,412,413],{"class":55,"line":227},[53,414,218],{},[53,416,417],{"class":55,"line":233},[53,418,224],{},[53,420,421],{"class":55,"line":239},[53,422,423],{},"      \u003CRoute path=\"\u002F\" element={ \u003CApp \u002F> } \u002F>\n",[53,425,426],{"class":55,"line":245},[53,427,428],{},"      \u003CRoute path=\"\u002Ftodolist\" element={ \u003CToDoList \u002F> } \u002F>\n",[53,430,432],{"class":55,"line":431},14,[53,433,236],{},[53,435,437],{"class":55,"line":436},15,[53,438,242],{},[53,440,442],{"class":55,"line":441},16,[53,443,248],{},[16,445,446,447,450,451,454],{},"接下來當你輸入 ",[39,448,449],{},"npm run dev"," 啟動專案，並在瀏覽器上輸入 ",[39,452,453],{},"http:\u002F\u002Flocalhost:3000\u002F#\u002Ftodolist"," 你會發現畫面一片空白，並且控制台會出現以下錯誤訊息",[44,456,458],{"className":46,"code":457,"language":48,"meta":49,"style":49},"Uncaught Error: A \u003CRoute> is only ever to be used as the child of \u003CRoutes> element, never rendered directly. Please wrap your \u003CRoute> in a \u003CRoutes>.\n",[39,459,460],{"__ignoreMap":49},[53,461,462],{"class":55,"line":56},[53,463,457],{},[16,465,466,467,470,471,474],{},"這邊我是刻意示範一個錯誤的寫法，其實簡單來講 ",[39,468,469],{},"\u003CRoute>"," 只能包在 ",[39,472,473],{},"\u003CRoutes>"," 底下使用，因此正確來講必須這樣寫才對",[44,476,478],{"className":166,"code":477,"language":168,"meta":49,"style":49},"import React from 'react'\nimport { HashRouter, Route, Routes } from \"react-router-dom\";\nimport ReactDOM from 'react-dom\u002Fclient'\nimport App from '.\u002FApp'\nimport '.\u002Findex.css'\nimport ToDoList from \".\u002FTodoList\";\n\nReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById('root')).render(\n  \u003CReact.StrictMode>\n    \u003CHashRouter>\n      \u003CRoutes>\n        \u003CRoute path=\"\u002F\" element={ \u003CApp \u002F> } \u002F>\n        \u003CRoute path=\"\u002Ftodolist\" element={ \u003CToDoList \u002F> } \u002F>\n      \u003C\u002FRoutes>\n    \u003C\u002FHashRouter>\n  \u003C\u002FReact.StrictMode>\n)\n",[39,479,480,484,489,493,497,501,505,509,513,517,521,526,531,536,541,545,549],{"__ignoreMap":49},[53,481,482],{"class":55,"line":56},[53,483,175],{},[53,485,486],{"class":55,"line":178},[53,487,488],{},"import { HashRouter, Route, Routes } from \"react-router-dom\";\n",[53,490,491],{"class":55,"line":184},[53,492,187],{},[53,494,495],{"class":55,"line":190},[53,496,193],{},[53,498,499],{"class":55,"line":196},[53,500,199],{},[53,502,503],{"class":55,"line":202},[53,504,402],{},[53,506,507],{"class":55,"line":209},[53,508,206],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":205},[53,510,511],{"class":55,"line":215},[53,512,212],{},[53,514,515],{"class":55,"line":221},[53,516,218],{},[53,518,519],{"class":55,"line":227},[53,520,224],{},[53,522,523],{"class":55,"line":233},[53,524,525],{},"      \u003CRoutes>\n",[53,527,528],{"class":55,"line":239},[53,529,530],{},"        \u003CRoute path=\"\u002F\" element={ \u003CApp \u002F> } \u002F>\n",[53,532,533],{"class":55,"line":245},[53,534,535],{},"        \u003CRoute path=\"\u002Ftodolist\" element={ \u003CToDoList \u002F> } \u002F>\n",[53,537,538],{"class":55,"line":431},[53,539,540],{},"      \u003C\u002FRoutes>\n",[53,542,543],{"class":55,"line":436},[53,544,236],{},[53,546,547],{"class":55,"line":441},[53,548,242],{},[53,550,552],{"class":55,"line":551},17,[53,553,248],{},[16,555,556,557,559],{},"接下來你重新 ",[39,558,449],{}," 的時候應該會看到滿空白的，只有很孤單寂寞覺得冷的一段話「App」，這是很正常的，因為首頁就是這樣子。",[16,561,562,563,566,567,569],{},"但...我們該如何進入 ",[39,564,565],{},"todolist"," 呢？你可以先試著在瀏覽器網址列輸入 ",[39,568,453],{},"，這樣子你就可以看到「ToDoList」出現在畫面上囉。",[16,571,572,573,75,576,579],{},"那麼今天就先到這邊結束，後面我們還會繼續講解 React Router 的其他使用方式，例如 巢狀路由、",[39,574,575],{},"Link",[39,577,578],{},"NavLink"," 等等。",[16,581,582,583],{},"範例程式碼：",[116,584,587],{"href":585,"rel":586},"https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fhsiangfeng\u002Fexample-vite-react\u002Ftree\u002Ffeature\u002Frouter-init",[120],"React Router Example",[12,589,590],{"id":590},"後記",[16,592,593],{},"本文將會同步更新到我的部落格",[295,595,596],{},[298,597,598],{},[116,599,602],{"href":600,"rel":601},"https:\u002F\u002Fisraynotarray.com\u002F",[120],"是 Ray 不是 Array",[604,605,606],"style",{},"html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}",{"title":49,"searchDepth":178,"depth":178,"links":608},[609,610,611,612,613],{"id":14,"depth":178,"text":14},{"id":21,"depth":178,"text":22},{"id":147,"depth":178,"text":148},{"id":254